{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775841728200,"sessionID":"ses_287965c48ffeBA0bj1XqfDCEYv","part":{"id":"prt_d786a4ca0001slObZyh5jSfvQC","messageID":"msg_d786a3520001FG7dN6SywtfGtc","sessionID":"ses_287965c48ffeBA0bj1XqfDCEYv","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-105817109fb2401e92ab6c8e431ae9bd","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-004/spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-004/spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架\n2: \n3: ## Metadata\n4: \n5: | Item | Value |\n6: |------|-------|\n7: | AR | AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 |\n8: | Module | `pkg/workloadmanager` |\n9: | Language | Go |\n10: | Size | M |\n11: | Stage | ST-0 |\n12: \n13: ## Scope\n14: \n15: 定义 WorkloadManager 的 HTTP 服务框架，包括:\n16: - HTTP 服务器配置与生命周期管理\n17: - 路由设计与中间件架构\n18: - 请求/响应数据结构定义\n19: - 健康检查与指标暴露端点\n20: - 错误处理与日志记录机制\n21: \n22: ## Out of Scope\n23: \n24: - 业务逻辑实现（Sandbox 创建、调度等）\n25: - WebSocket 连接管理\n26: - 认证授权实现\n27: - 具体业务 API 端点实现\n28: \n29: ## Dependencies\n30: \n31: - `net/http` 标准库\n32: - 可能的第三方 HTTP 路由库（待设计确认）\n33: - 日志库（pkg/logging 或第三方）\n34: \n35: ## Deliverables\n36: \n37: | File | Description |\n38: |------|-------------|\n39: | `pkg/workloadmanager/server.go` | HTTP 服务器核心实现 |\n40: | `pkg/workloadmanager/router.go` | 路由配置与中间件 |\n41: | `pkg/workloadmanager/handlers/` | Handler 接口与基础实现 |\n42: | `pkg/workloadmanager/middleware/` | 中间件实现 |\n43: \n44: ## Acceptance Criteria\n45: \n46: - [ ] HTTP 服务器支持优雅启动和关闭\n47: - [ ] 路由框架可扩展，支持标准 RESTful API\n48: - [ ] 中间件链可配置\n49: - [ ] 健康检查端点可访问\n50: - [ ] 错误响应格式统一\n51: - [ ] 通过 `go vet` 和 `golangci-lint`\n52: \n53: ## References\n54: \n55: - Go net/http 文档: https://pkg.go.dev/net/http\n\n(End of file - total 55 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 |\n| Module | `pkg/workloadmanager` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | M |\n| Stage | ST-0 |\n\n## Scope\n\n定义 WorkloadManager 的 HTTP 服务框架，包括:\n- HTTP 服务器配置与生命周期管理\n- 路由设计与中间件架构\n- 请求/响应数据结构定义\n- 健康检查与指标暴露端点\n- 错误处理与日志记录机制","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-004/spec.md","time":{"start":1775841728181,"end":1775841728199}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775841728202,"sessionID":"ses_287965c48ffeBA0bj1XqfDCEYv","part":{"id":"prt_d786a4fb2001U04PNkPo2ZHVGh","messageID":"msg_d786a3520001FG7dN6SywtfGtc","sessionID":"ses_287965c48ffeBA0bj1XqfDCEYv","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-90da99721fb2408e94c83a27363d4359","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-004/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-004/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 Design\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: | Item | Value |\n6: |------|-------|\n7: | AR | AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 |\n8: | Module | `pkg/workloadmanager` |\n9: | Language | Go |\n10: | Size | M |\n11: | Stage | ST-1 |\n12: \n13: 定义 WorkloadManager 的 HTTP 服务框架，提供 RESTful API 基础设施、中间件架构、生命周期管理。\n14: \n15: ## Design\n16: \n17: ### Architecture\n18: \n19: ```\n20: cmd/workload-manager/\n21:     └── main.go                    — 入口，调用 pkg/workloadmanager\n22: pkg/workloadmanager/\n23:     ├── server.go                  — HTTPServer 核心实现\n24:     ├── router.go                  — 路由配置与路由组\n25:     ├── config.go                  — 配置结构体\n26:     ├── types.go                   — 公共类型定义\n27:     ├── handlers/\n28:     │   ├── handler.go             — Handler 接口\n29:     │   └── health.go              — 健康检查实现\n30:     └── middleware/\n31:         ├── logging.go             — 请求日志中间件\n32:         ├── recovery.go            — Panic 恢复中间件\n33:         └── cors.go                — CORS 中间件\n34: ```\n35: \n36: ### Dependencies\n37: \n38: | Package | Purpose |\n39: |---------|---------|\n40: | `net/http` | 标准库 HTTP 服务器 |\n41: | `context` | 请求上下文 |\n42: | `sync` | 并发控制（优雅关闭） |\n43: | `os/signal` | 信号处理 |\n44: | `time` | 超时配置 |\n45: \n46: ### Router Library Selection\n47: \n48: **决策**: 使用 `go-chi/chi` v5\n49: \n50: | Aspect | Rationale |\n51: |--------|-----------|\n52: | 零外部依赖 | 仅依赖 Go 标准库 |\n53: | 兼容 net/http | 可使用所有标准库中间件 |\n54: | 路由分组 | 支持路由组与中间件作用域 |\n55: | 性能 | 足够优秀（参考 benchmark） |\n56: \n57: ## Data Structures\n58: \n59: ### server.go\n60: \n61: ```go\n62: type HTTPServer struct {\n63:     server   *http.Server\n64:     router   chi.Router\n65:     config   Config\n66:     handlers map[string]Handler\n67:     logger   Logger\n68:     stopCh   chan struct{}\n69: }\n70: \n71: type Config struct {\n72:     Addr              string        // 监听地址，如 \":8080\"\n73:     ReadTimeout       time.Duration // 读超时\n74:     WriteTimeout      time.Duration // 写超时\n75:     IdleTimeout       time.Duration // 空闲连接超时\n76:     ShutdownTimeout   time.Duration // 优雅关闭超时\n77:     EnableHealthz     bool          // 是否启用健康检查\n78:     EnableReadyz      bool          // 是否启用就绪探针\n79: }\n80: ```\n81: \n82: ### router.go\n83: \n84: ```go\n85: type Router struct {\n86:     chi.Router\n87: }\n88: \n89: func NewRouter() *Router {\n90:     r := chi.NewRouter()\n91:     return &Router{Router: r}\n92: }\n93: \n94: func (r *Router) RegisterHandlers(handlers ...Handler) {\n95:     for _, h := range handlers {\n96:         h.Register(r.Router)\n97:     }\n98: }\n99: ```\n100: \n101: ### handlers/handler.go\n102: \n103: ```go\n104: type Handler interface {\n105:     Register(r chi.Router)\n106: }\n107: \n108: type HandlerFunc func(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) error\n109: \n110: func (hf HandlerFunc) ServeHTTP(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) {\n111:     if err := hf(w, r); err != nil {\n112:         HandleError(w, r, err)\n113:     }\n114: }\n115: ```\n116: \n117: ### handlers/health.go\n118: \n119: ```go\n120: type HealthHandler struct {\n121:     checker HealthChecker\n122: }\n123: \n124: type HealthChecker interface {\n125:     IsHealthy() bool\n126:     IsReady() bool\n127: }\n128: \n129: func (h *HealthHandler) Register(r chi.Router) {\n130:     r.Get(\"/healthz\", h.healthz)\n131:     r.Get(\"/readyz\", h.readyz)\n132: }\n133: \n134: func (h *HealthHandler) healthz(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) {\n135:     w.WriteHeader(http.StatusOK)\n136:     json.NewEncoder(w).Encode(map[string]string{\"status\": \"ok\"})\n137: }\n138: \n139: func (h *HealthHandler) readyz(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) {\n140:     if h.checker == nil || !h.checker.IsReady() {\n141:         w.WriteHeader(http.StatusServiceUnavailable)\n142:         json.NewEncoder(w).Encode(map[string]string{\"status\": \"not ready\"})\n143:         return\n144:     }\n145:     w.WriteHeader(http.StatusOK)\n146:     json.NewEncoder(w).Encode(map[string]string{\"status\": \"ready\"})\n147: }\n148: ```\n149: \n150: ### middleware/logging.go\n151: \n152: ```go\n153: type LoggingMiddleware struct {\n154:     logger Logger\n155: }\n156: \n157: func (m *LoggingMiddleware) Wrap(next http.Handler) http.Handler {\n158:     return http.HandlerFunc(func(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) {\n159:         start := time.Now()\n160:         \n161:         ww := &responseWriterWrapper{ResponseWriter: w}\n162:         next.ServeHTTP(ww, r)\n163:         \n164:         m.logger.Info(\"request\",\n165:             \"method\", r.Method,\n166:             \"path\", r.URL.Path,\n167:             \"status\", ww.status,\n168:             \"duration\", time.Since(start),\n169:         )\n170:     })\n171: }\n172: ```\n173: \n174: ### middleware/recovery.go\n175: \n176: ```go\n177: type RecoveryMiddleware struct {\n178:     logger Logger\n179: }\n180: \n181: func (m *RecoveryMiddleware) Wrap(next http.Handler) http.Handler {\n182:     return http.HandlerFunc(func(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) {\n183:         defer func() {\n184:             if err := recover(); err != nil {\n185:                 m.logger.Error(\"panic recovered\", \"error\", err, \"path\", r.URL.Path)\n186:                 http.Error(w, \"Internal Server Error\", http.StatusInternalServerError)\n187:             }\n188:         }()\n189:         next.ServeHTTP(w, r)\n190:     })\n191: }\n192: ```\n193: \n194: ### types.go\n195: \n196: ```go\n197: type ErrorResponse struct {\n198:     Code    string `json:\"code\"`\n199:     Message string `json:\"message\"`\n200:     Details any    `json:\"details,omitempty\"`\n201: }\n202: \n203: type SuccessResponse struct {\n204:     Data any `json:\"data\"`\n205: }\n206: \n207: func HandleError(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request, err error) {\n208:     // 根据 error 类型映射到 HTTP 状态码\n209:     // 统一返回 ErrorResponse JSON\n210: }\n211: ```\n212: \n213: ## API Endpoints\n214: \n215: ### Health Endpoints\n216: \n217: | Endpoint | Method | Purpose |\n218: |----------|--------|---------|\n219: | `/healthz` | GET | 健康检查（Kubernetes liveness probe） |\n220: | `/readyz` | GET | 就绪探针（Kubernetes readiness probe） |\n221: \n222: ### API Group\n223: \n224: | Prefix | Purpose |\n225: |--------|---------|\n226: | `/api/v1` | 业务 API 路由组（待后续 AR 实现） |\n227: \n228: ### Middleware Chain\n229: \n230: ```\n231: Recovery → Logging → CORS (optional) → Business Handler\n232: ```\n233: \n234: ## Error Handling\n235: \n236: | Error Type | HTTP Status | Error Code |\n237: |------------|-------------|------------|\n238: | Validation Error | 400 | `VALIDATION_ERROR` |\n239: | Not Found | 404 | `NOT_FOUND` |\n240: | Internal Error | 500 | `INTERNAL_ERROR` |\n241: | Service Unavailable | 503 | `SERVICE_UNAVAILABLE` |\n242: \n243: 统一错误响应格式:\n244: ```json\n245: {\n246:   \"code\": \"VALIDATION_ERROR\",\n247:   \"message\": \"Invalid request parameter\",\n248:   \"details\": {\"field\": \"name\", \"reason\": \"required\"}\n249: }\n250: ```\n251: \n252: ## Testing Strategy\n253: \n254: ### Unit Tests\n255: \n256: | Test Category | Coverage |\n257: |---------------|----------|\n258: | HTTPServer 启动/关闭 | 测试优雅关闭逻辑 |\n259: | HealthHandler | 测试 `/healthz` 和 `/readyz` 端点 |\n260: | Middleware | 测试日志、恢复、CORS 中间件 |\n261: | 错误处理 | 测试 HandleError 返回正确的 JSON 格式 |\n262: \n263: ### Integration Tests\n264: \n265: | Test | Description |\n266: |------|-------------|\n267: | 端到端请求 | 启动真实 HTTP 服务器，发送请求并验证响应 |\n268: | 中间件链 | 验证中间件按预期顺序执行 |\n269: \n270: ### Test File Structure\n271: \n272: ```\n273: pkg/workloadmanager/\n274:   server_test.go\n275:   router_test.go\n276:   handlers/health_test.go\n277:   middleware/logging_test.go\n278:   middleware/recovery_test.go\n279: ```\n280: \n281: ## File Structure\n282: \n283: ```\n284: pkg/workloadmanager/\n285:   server.go              — HTTPServer 实现\n286:   router.go              — Router 封装\n287:   config.go              — Config 结构体\n288:   types.go               — 公共类型定义\n289:   handlers/\n290:     handler.go           — Handler 接口\n291:     health.go            — HealthHandler 实现\n292:   middleware/\n293:     logging.go           — 日志中间件\n294:     recovery.go          — Panic 恢复中间件\n295:     cors.go              — CORS 中间件\n296: ```\n297: \n298: ## Open Questions\n299: \n300: - 是否需要 WebSocket 支持？（暂不在范围内，待后续 AR）\n301: - 是否需要限流中间件？（暂不在范围内，待后续 AR）\n302: - 日志库选型：pkg/logging 还是第三方（如 zap、logrus）？\n303: - 指标端点 `/metrics` 是否在本 AR 范围内？（建议预留路由，实现待后续 AR）\n304: \n305: ## References\n306: \n307: - chi router: https://github.com/go-chi/chi\n308: - Go net/http: https://pkg.go.dev/net/http\n309: - Kubernetes API conventions: https://git.k8s.io/community/contributors/devel/sig-architecture/api-conventions.md\n\n(End of file - total 309 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 Design\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 |\n| Module | `pkg/workloadmanager` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | M |\n| Stage | ST-1 |\n\n定义 WorkloadManager 的 HTTP 服务框架，提供 RESTful API 基础设施、中间件架构、生命周期管理。\n\n## Design\n\n### Architecture\n\n```\ncmd/workload-manager/","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-004/design.md","time":{"start":1775841728184,"end":1775841728201}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775841728204,"sessionID":"ses_287965c48ffeBA0bj1XqfDCEYv","part":{"id":"prt_d786a5353001HrnioGWWYpJ5Qt","messageID":"msg_d786a3520001FG7dN6SywtfGtc","sessionID":"ses_287965c48ffeBA0bj1XqfDCEYv","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-f479f2fbed8c4c38898c0bfd22dff6a3","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-004/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-004/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 Proposal\n2: \n3: ## Purpose\n4: \n5: 为 WorkloadManager 构建 HTTP 服务框架，作为 agentcube 核心服务器的网络层基础，提供:\n6: \n7: 1. **RESTful API 基础设施**: 支持 Sandbox、SandboxClaim、Session 等资源的 CRUD 操作\n8: 2. **中间件架构**: 提供请求日志、认证、限流、CORS 等可插拔能力\n9: 3. **生命周期管理**: 优雅启动、信号处理、连接清理\n10: 4. **可观测性**: 健康检查、就绪探针、Prometheus 指标端点\n11: 5. **错误处理**: 统一的错误响应格式与日志记录\n12: \n13: ## Scope\n14: \n15: ### In Scope\n16: \n17: | Deliverable | Description |\n18: |-------------|-------------|\n19: | `pkg/workloadmanager/server.go` | HTTP 服务器核心实现，包括启动、关闭、配置 |\n20: | `pkg/workloadmanager/router.go` | 路由初始化与路由组管理 |\n21: | `pkg/workloadmanager/handlers/base.go` | 基础 Handler 接口定义 |\n22: | `pkg/workloadmanager/handlers/health.go` | 健康检查与就绪探针实现 |\n23: | `pkg/workloadmanager/middleware/logging.go` | 请求日志中间件 |\n24: | `pkg/workloadmanager/middleware/recovery.go` | Panic 恢复中间件 |\n25: | `pkg/workloadmanager/middleware/cors.go` | CORS 中间件（可选） |\n26: | `pkg/workloadmanager/types.go` | 请求/响应数据结构定义 |\n27: \n28: ### API Endpoints Framework\n29: \n30: ```\n31: /api/v1/\n32: ├── healthz          — 健康检查 (GET)\n33: ├── readyz           — 就绪探针 (GET)\n34: ├── sandboxes        — Sandbox CRUD (待后续 AR 实现)\n35: ├── sandboxclaims    — SandboxClaim CRUD (待后续 AR 实现)\n36: └── sessions         — Session 管理 (待后续 AR 实现)\n37: ```\n38: \n39: ### Out of Scope\n40: \n41: - 业务 Handler 实现（Sandbox、SandboxClaim、Session）\n42: - WebSocket 路由与连接管理\n43: - 认证授权逻辑\n44: - 具体的限流策略实现\n45: - 数据库/存储层集成\n46: \n47: ## Impact Analysis\n48: \n49: ### Upstream Dependencies\n50: \n51: | Dependency | Impact |\n52: |------------|--------|\n53: | Go 标准库 `net/http` | 核心依赖 |\n54: | 可能的第三方路由库（如 chi, gorilla/mux） | 待设计决策，可选 |\n55: \n56: ### Downstream Consumers\n57: \n58: | Consumer | Usage |\n59: |----------|-------|\n60: | WorkloadManager 业务逻辑 | 通过 Handler 接口注册业务逻辑 |\n61: | 监控系统 | 通过 `/metrics` 端点采集指标 |\n62: | Kubernetes 探针 | 通过 `/healthz`, `/readyz` 检查服务状态 |\n63: | 客户端应用 | 通过 RESTful API 访问服务 |\n64: \n65: ### Breaking Change Considerations\n66: \n67: - **路由路径变更**: API 路径设计影响所有客户端\n68: - **错误格式变更**: 统一错误响应格式影响客户端错误处理逻辑\n69: - **中间件顺序**: 中间件执行顺序可能影响请求处理流程\n70: \n71: ## Alternatives Considered\n72: \n73: ### Alternative 1: 使用标准库 net/http\n74: \n75: **Approach**: 仅使用 `net/http` 标准库，手动实现路由与中间件。\n76: \n77: | Aspect | Evaluation |\n78: |--------|------------|\n79: | Pros | 无外部依赖；完全控制；性能最优 |\n80: | Cons | 路由功能有限；需要手动实现中间件链；缺乏社区生态 |\n81: \n82: **Decision**: 待评估。对于简单场景可行，但路由分组、路径参数等功能需要额外实现。\n83: \n84: ### Alternative 2: 使用 gorilla/mux\n85: \n86: **Approach**: 使用成熟的 `gorilla/mux` 路由库。\n87: \n88: | Aspect | Evaluation |\n89: |--------|------------|\n90: | Pros | 功能完善；社区活跃；中间件支持好 |\n91: | Cons | 外部依赖；性能略逊于 chi |\n92: \n93: **Decision**: 可选方案。\n94: \n95: ### Alternative 3: 使用 chi 路由器\n96: \n97: **Approach**: 使用轻量级 `chi` 路由器。\n98: \n99: | Aspect | Evaluation |\n100: |--------|------------|\n101: | Pros | 零依赖；性能优秀；兼容 net/http；内置中间件 |\n102: | Cons | 社区规模小于 gorilla/mux |\n103: \n104: **Decision**: 推荐。chi 轻量且符合 Go 惯例。\n105: \n106: ### Alternative 4: 使用 Gin/Echo 框架\n107: \n108: **Approach**: 使用完整 Web 框架（Gin 或 Echo）。\n109: \n110: | Aspect | Evaluation |\n111: |--------|------------|\n112: | Pros | 功能全面；性能优秀；生态丰富 |\n113: | Cons | 过度封装；违反 AgentCube 渐进式设计原则 |\n114: \n115: **Decision**: 拒绝。AgentCube 倾向于使用标准库 + 轻量级工具，而非重型框架。\n116: \n117: ## Risks\n118: \n119: | Risk | Mitigation |\n120: |------|------------|\n121: | 路由库选型错误 | 设计阶段充分评估 chi/gorilla/mux/stdlib，保留切换能力 |\n122: | 中间件顺序导致 Bug | 明确中间件执行顺序文档，添加集成测试 |\n123: | 错误响应格式不统一 | 定义 Error 结构体，所有 Handler 使用统一错误返回方法 |\n124: | 性能瓶颈 | 基准测试关键端点，监控 p99 延迟 |\n125: \n126: ## Implementation Notes\n127: \n128: 1. **配置**: 使用环境变量或配置文件指定端口、超时等参数\n129: 2. **日志**: 集成 pkg/logging，记录请求 ID、路径、状态码、延迟\n130: 3. **优雅关闭**: 监听 SIGTERM/SIGINT，等待现有连接完成（最长 30s）\n131: 4. **健康检查**: `/healthz` 总是返回 200，`/readyz` 检查依赖服务状态\n132: 5. **中间件模式**: 使用 Go 标准中间件签名 `func(http.Handler) http.Handler`\n133: \n134: ## References\n135: \n136: - Go net/http: https://pkg.go.dev/net/http\n137: - chi router: https://github.com/go-chi/chi\n138: - Kubernetes Healthz Pattern: https://kubernetes.io/docs/tasks/configure-pod-container/configure-liveness-readiness-probes/\n\n(End of file - total 138 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 Proposal\n\n## Purpose\n\n为 WorkloadManager 构建 HTTP 服务框架，作为 agentcube 核心服务器的网络层基础，提供:\n\n1. **RESTful API 基础设施**: 支持 Sandbox、SandboxClaim、Session 等资源的 CRUD 操作\n2. **中间件架构**: 提供请求日志、认证、限流、CORS 等可插拔能力\n3. **生命周期管理**: 优雅启动、信号处理、连接清理\n4. **可观测性**: 健康检查、就绪探针、Prometheus 指标端点\n5. **错误处理**: 统一的错误响应格式与日志记录\n\n## Scope\n\n### In Scope\n\n| Deliverable | Description |\n|-------------|-------------|\n| `pkg/workloadmanager/server.go` | HTTP 服务器核心实现，包括启动、关闭、配置 |\n| `pkg/workloadmanager/router.go` | 路由初始化与路由组管理 |","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-004/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775841728186,"end":1775841728203}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775841728207,"sessionID":"ses_287965c48ffeBA0bj1XqfDCEYv","part":{"id":"prt_d786a5699001L9ENRspzoxzQXY","messageID":"msg_d786a3520001FG7dN6SywtfGtc","sessionID":"ses_287965c48ffeBA0bj1XqfDCEYv","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-8ce34cf94b594072a24fc778b7cc580b","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-002/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-002/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Delta Spec: AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter Type Definition\n2: \n3: **Module:** `pkg/apis`  \n4: **Language:** Go  \n5: **Size:** S\n6: \n7: ---\n8: \n9: ## GIVEN/WHEN/THEN Scenarios\n10: \n11: ### Requirement: Package structure and registration\n12: \n13: The system SHALL define the `CodeInterpreter` and `CodeInterpreterList` types in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` with proper package structure, scheme registration, and CRD markers for controller-gen.\n14: \n15: #### Scenario: Package structure exists\n16: - **GIVEN** the repository root at `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube`\n17: - **WHEN** examining `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n18: - **THEN** the directory SHALL contain:\n19:   - `doc.go` with `+k8s:deepcopy-gen=package` marker\n20:   - `register.go` with `SchemeGroupVersion` set to `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`\n21:   - `codeinterpreter_types.go` with `CodeInterpreter` and `CodeInterpreterList` types\n22:   - `shared_types.go` with `AuthModeType` enum and `TargetPort` type\n23:   - `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` (generated)\n24: \n25: #### Scenario: Scheme group version is correct\n26: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/groupversion_info.go`\n27: - **WHEN** reading the file\n28: - **THEN** `GroupVersion` SHALL be `schema.GroupVersion{Group: \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", Version: \"v1alpha1\"}`\n29: \n30: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreter Kind registration\n31: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go`\n32: - **WHEN** reading the file\n33: - **THEN** `CodeInterpreterKind` SHALL be `\"CodeInterpreter\"`\n34: - AND `CodeInterpreterListKind` SHALL be `\"CodeInterpreterList\"`\n35: - AND `CodeInterpreterGroupVersionKind` SHALL be `GroupVersion.WithKind(\"CodeInterpreter\")`\n36: \n37: ---\n38: \n39: ### Requirement: CodeInterpreter type definition\n40: \n41: The system SHALL define `CodeInterpreter` as a Kubernetes-style typed object with `TypeMeta`, `ObjectMeta`, `Spec`, and `Status`.\n42: \n43: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreter struct shape\n44: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n45: - **WHEN** reading the `CodeInterpreter` struct definition\n46: - **THEN** the struct SHALL embed `metav1.TypeMeta` and `metav1.ObjectMeta` and have `Spec CodeInterpreterSpec` and `Status CodeInterpreterStatus` fields with JSON tags `spec` and `status`\n47: \n48: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreterList struct shape\n49: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n50: - **WHEN** reading the `CodeInterpreterList` struct definition\n51: - **THEN** the struct SHALL embed `metav1.TypeMeta`, have `metav1.ListMeta` with JSON tag `metadata`, and `Items []CodeInterpreter` with JSON tag `items`\n52: \n53: #### Scenario: CRD markers on CodeInterpreter\n54: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n55: - **WHEN** examining type-level markers\n56: - **THEN** the `CodeInterpreter` type SHALL have:\n57:   - `+genclient` marker\n58:   - `+k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object` marker\n59:   - `+kubebuilder:object:root=true` marker\n60:   - `+kubebuilder:subresource:status` marker\n61:   - `+kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced` marker\n62:   - `+kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"` marker\n63: \n64: ---\n65: \n66: ### Requirement: CodeInterpreterSpec definition\n67: \n68: The system SHALL define `CodeInterpreterSpec` with fields for sandbox template, session management, warm pool, and authentication.\n69: \n70: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreterSpec fields\n71: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n72: - **WHEN** reading the `CodeInterpreterSpec` struct\n73: - **THEN** the struct SHALL contain fields:\n74:   - `Ports []TargetPort` with JSON tag `ports` (optional)\n75:   - `Template *CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate` with JSON tag `template` (required)\n76:   - `SessionTimeout *metav1.Duration` with JSON tag `sessionTimeout` (optional, default 15m)\n77:   - `MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration` with JSON tag `maxSessionDuration` (optional, default 8h)\n78:   - `WarmPoolSize *int32` with JSON tag `warmPoolSize` (optional)\n79:   - `AuthMode AuthModeType` with JSON tag `authMode` (optional, default picod)\n80: \n81: #### Scenario: Template field is required\n82: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n83: - **WHEN** examining the `Template` field markers\n84: - **THEN** it SHALL have `+kubebuilder:validation:Required` marker\n85: \n86: #### Scenario: SessionTimeout default\n87: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n88: - **WHEN** examining the `SessionTimeout` field marker\n89: - **THEN** it SHALL have `+kubebuilder:default=\"15m\"` marker\n90: \n91: #### Scenario: MaxSessionDuration default\n92: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n93: - **WHEN** examining the `MaxSessionDuration` field marker\n94: - **THEN** it SHALL have `+kubebuilder:default=\"8h\"` marker\n95: \n96: #### Scenario: AuthMode enum and default\n97: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n98: - **WHEN** examining the `AuthMode` field marker\n99: - **THEN** it SHALL have:\n100:   - `+kubebuilder:default=picod` marker\n101:   - `+kubebuilder:validation:Enum=picod;none` marker\n102: \n103: ---\n104: \n105: ### Requirement: CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate definition\n106: \n107: The system SHALL define `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate` for configuring code interpreter pods.\n108: \n109: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate fields\n110: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n111: - **WHEN** reading the `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate` struct\n112: - **THEN** the struct SHALL contain:\n113:   - `Labels map[string]string` with JSON tag `labels` (optional)\n114:   - `Annotations map[string]string` with JSON tag `annotations` (optional)\n115:   - `RuntimeClassName *string` with JSON tag `runtimeClassName` (optional)\n116:   - `Image string` with JSON tag `image` (optional)\n117:   - `ImagePullPolicy corev1.PullPolicy` with JSON tag `imagePullPolicy` (optional)\n118:   - `ImagePullSecrets []corev1.LocalObjectReference` with JSON tag `imagePullSecrets` (optional)\n119:   - `Environment []corev1.EnvVar` with JSON tag `environment` (optional)\n120:   - `Command []string` with JSON tag `command` (optional)\n121:   - `Args []string` with JSON tag `args` (optional)\n122:   - `Resources corev1.ResourceRequirements` with JSON tag `resources` (optional)\n123: \n124: #### Scenario: ImagePullSecrets list markers\n125: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n126: - **WHEN** examining the `ImagePullSecrets` field\n127: - **THEN** it SHALL have:\n128:   - `+patchMergeKey=name` marker\n129:   - `+patchStrategy=merge` marker\n130:   - `+listType=map` marker\n131:   - `+listMapKey=name` marker\n132: \n133: ---\n134: \n135: ### Requirement: CodeInterpreterStatus definition\n136: \n137: The system SHALL define `CodeInterpreterStatus` with conditions and readiness flag.\n138: \n139: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreterStatus fields\n140: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n141: - **WHEN** reading the `CodeInterpreterStatus` struct\n142: - **THEN** the struct SHALL contain:\n143:   - `Conditions []metav1.Condition` with JSON tag `conditions` (optional)\n144:   - `Ready bool` with JSON tag `ready` (optional)\n145: \n146: #### Scenario: Conditions field markers\n147: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n148: - **WHEN** examining the `Conditions` field\n149: - **THEN** it SHALL have:\n150:   - `+optional` marker\n151:   - `+listType=atomic` marker\n152: \n153: ---\n154: \n155: ### Requirement: AuthModeType enum definition\n156: \n157: The system SHALL define `AuthModeType` in `shared_types.go` as an enum for authentication modes.\n158: \n159: #### Scenario: AuthModeType type definition\n160: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go`\n161: - **WHEN** reading the file\n162: - **THEN** `AuthModeType` SHALL be defined as `type AuthModeType string`\n163: \n164: #### Scenario: AuthModeType constants\n165: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go`\n166: - **WHEN** reading the file\n167: - **THEN** the following constants SHALL be defined:\n168:   - `AuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"`\n169:   - `AuthModeNone AuthModeType = \"none\"`\n170: \n171: ---\n172: \n173: ### Requirement: DeepCopy generation\n174: \n175: The system SHALL generate `DeepCopy` methods for all types using controller-gen.\n176: \n177: #### Scenario: DeepCopyInto for CodeInterpreter\n178: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go` (after `make generate`)\n179: - **WHEN** examining generated code\n180: - **THEN** `func (in *CodeInterpreter) DeepCopyInto(out *CodeInterpreter)` SHALL exist and correctly copy all nested fields\n181: \n182: #### Scenario: DeepCopyInto for CodeInterpreterList\n183: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go`\n184: - **WHEN** examining generated code\n185: - **THEN** `func (in *CodeInterpreterList) DeepCopyInto(out *CodeInterpreterList)` SHALL exist and correctly copy `Items` slice\n186: \n187: #### Scenario: DeepCopyInto for CodeInterpreterSpec\n188: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go`\n189: - **WHEN** examining generated code\n190: - **THEN** `func (in *CodeInterpreterSpec) DeepCopyInto(out *CodeInterpreterSpec)` SHALL exist and correctly copy pointer fields including `Template`, `SessionTimeout`, `MaxSessionDuration`, and `WarmPoolSize`\n191: \n192: #### Scenario: DeepCopyInto for CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate\n193: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go`\n194: - **WHEN** examining generated code\n195: - **THEN** `func (in *CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate) DeepCopyInto(out *CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate)` SHALL exist\n196: \n197: #### Scenario: DeepCopyInto for CodeInterpreterStatus\n198: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go`\n199: - **WHEN** examining generated code\n200: - **THEN** `func (in *CodeInterpreterStatus) DeepCopyInto(out *CodeInterpreterStatus)` SHALL exist\n201: \n202: #### Scenario: DeepCopyObject implementation\n203: - **GIVEN** the `CodeInterpreter` and `CodeInterpreterList` types\n204: - **WHEN** the DeepCopy methods are generated\n205: - **THEN** both types SHALL implement `runtime.Object` interface via `DeepCopyObject()` method\n206: \n207: ---\n208: \n209: ### Requirement: Client-go code generation compatibility\n210: \n211: The system SHALL define types compatible with `k8s.io/code-generator` for generating typed clients, informers, and listers for CodeInterpreter.\n212: \n213: #### Scenario: Generated typed client for CodeInterpreter\n214: - **GIVEN** client-go code generation completed\n215: - **WHEN** examining `client-go/clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go`\n216: - **THEN** `CodeInterpreterInterface` SHALL define methods: `Create`, `Update`, `UpdateStatus`, `Delete`, `DeleteCollection`, `Get`, `List`, `Watch`, `Patch`\n217: \n218: #### Scenario: CodeInterpretersGetter interface\n219: - **GIVEN** client-go code generation completed\n220: - **WHEN** examining `client-go/clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/runtime_client.go`\n221: - **THEN** `RuntimeV1alpha1Interface` SHALL include `CodeInterpretersGetter`\n222: \n223: #### Scenario: Generated informer for CodeInterpreter\n224: - **GIVEN** client-go code generation completed\n225: - **WHEN** examining `client-go/informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go`\n226: - **THEN** `CodeInterpreterInformer` interface SHALL define `Informer() cache.SharedIndexInformer` and `Lister() runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreterLister`\n227: \n228: #### Scenario: Generated lister for CodeInterpreter\n229: - **GIVEN** client-go code generation completed\n230: - **WHEN** examining `client-go/listers/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go`\n231: - **THEN** `CodeInterpreterLister` interface SHALL define `List(selector labels.Selector)` and `CodeInterpreters(namespace string)` methods\n232: \n233: #### Scenario: REST resource plural\n234: - **GIVEN** the generated typed client for CodeInterpreter\n235: - **WHEN** examining `client-go/clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go`\n236: - **THEN** the REST resource plural SHALL be `codeinterpreters`\n237: \n238: ---\n239: \n240: ### Requirement: JSON serialization\n241: \n242: The system SHALL ensure all types serialize correctly to/from JSON with camelCase field names.\n243: \n244: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreter JSON serialization\n245: - **GIVEN** a `CodeInterpreter` instance with all fields populated\n246: - **WHEN** serializing to JSON\n247: - **THEN** the output SHALL use camelCase field names: `sessionTimeout`, `maxSessionDuration`, `warmPoolSize`, `authMode`, `pathPrefix`\n248: \n249: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreter JSON deserialization\n250: - **GIVEN** a JSON document with camelCase field names\n251: - **WHEN** deserializing to `CodeInterpreter`\n252: - **THEN** all fields SHALL be correctly populated including nested `Template` and `Ports` slice\n253: \n254: #### Scenario: Default values applied on deserialization\n255: - **GIVEN** a JSON document without `sessionTimeout`, `maxSessionDuration`, and `authMode` fields\n256: - **WHEN** deserializing to `CodeInterpreterSpec` with defaulting enabled\n257: - **THEN** `SessionTimeout` SHALL default to `15m`\n258: - AND `MaxSessionDuration` SHALL default to `8h`\n259: - AND `AuthMode` SHALL default to `picod`\n260: \n261: ---\n262: \n263: ### Requirement: List type markers\n264: \n265: The system SHALL use correct Kubernetes list type markers for slice fields.\n266: \n267: #### Scenario: Ports list type\n268: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n269: - **WHEN** examining the `Ports` field in `CodeInterpreterSpec`\n270: - **THEN** it SHALL have `+listType=atomic` marker\n271: \n272: #### Scenario: Conditions list type\n273: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n274: - **WHEN** examining the `Conditions` field in `CodeInterpreterStatus`\n275: - **THEN** it SHALL have `+listType=atomic` marker\n276: \n277: #### Scenario: Environment list type\n278: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n279: - **WHEN** examining the `Environment` field in `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate`\n280: - **THEN** it SHALL have `+listType=atomic` marker\n281: \n282: #### Scenario: Command list type\n283: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n284: - **WHEN** examining the `Command` field in `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate`\n285: - **THEN** it SHALL have `+listType=atomic` marker\n286: \n287: #### Scenario: Args list type\n288: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n289: - **WHEN** examining the `Args` field in `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate`\n290: - **THEN** it SHALL have `+listType=atomic` marker\n\n(End of file - total 290 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Delta Spec: AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter Type Definition\n\n**Module:** `pkg/apis`  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** S\n\n---\n\n## GIVEN/WHEN/THEN Scenarios\n\n### Requirement: Package structure and registration\n\nThe system SHALL define the `CodeInterpreter` and `CodeInterpreterList` types in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` with proper package structure, scheme registration, and CRD markers for controller-gen.\n\n#### Scenario: Package structure exists\n- **GIVEN** the repository root at `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube`\n- **WHEN** examining `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n- **THEN** the directory SHALL contain:\n  - `doc.go` with `+k8s:deepcopy-gen=package` marker\n  - `register.go` with `SchemeGroupVersion` set to `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-002/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775841728188,"end":1775841728204}}}}
